<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-26-0138 </DOCNO><TEXT>The authors introduce to us the computer-supported control of load groupsvia sound frequency RF systems as an independent complex of the new on-linecontrol station in Frankfurt/Hoechst. They describe the short-term forecastnecessary for doing this and present a tested switching algorithm forenergy control. The article on the performance of the system is completedby a general view at the software formation, on-line data processing,information presentation and operational functions.</TEXT></DOC>